name: mapreduce.reduce.shuffle.parallelcopies
description:
The default number of parallel transfers run by reduce
  during the copy(shuffle) phase.

name: dfs.datanode.handler.count
description: The number of server threads for the datanode.

name: mapreduce.task.exit.timeout.check-interval-ms
description:
The interval in milliseconds between which the MR framework
  checks if task attempts stay in finishing state for too long.

name: dfs.qjournal.select-input-streams.timeout.ms
description: Timeout in milliseconds for accepting streams from JournalManagers.

name: dfs.client.socketcache.expiryMsec
description: Socket cache expiration for short-circuit reads in msec.

name: mapreduce.jobhistory.jobname.limit
description: Number of characters allowed for job name in Job History Server web page.

name: dfs.namenode.get-blocks.max-qps
description:
The maximum number of getBlocks RPCs data movement utilities can make to
    a NameNode per second. Values less than or equal to 0 disable throttling.
    This affects anything that uses a NameNodeConnector, i.e., the Balancer,
    Mover, and StoragePolicySatisfier.

name: mapreduce.shuffle.transfer.buffer.size
description:
This property is used only if
  mapreduce.shuffle.transferTo.allowed is set to false. In that case,
  this property defines the size of the buffer used in the buffer copy code
  for the shuffle phase. The size of this buffer determines the size of the IO
  requests.

name: dfs.webhdfs.netty.high.watermark
description: High watermark configuration to Netty for Datanode WebHdfs.

name: dfs.ha.zkfc.port
description:
The port number that the zookeeper failover controller RPC
    server binds to.
